WEBVTT

00:00.640 --> 00:02.360
The Eunuch has long served by Father's side

00:03.000 --> 00:04.040
As a son

00:04.480 --> 00:05.520
Wishing to show filial piety in the future

00:07.400 --> 00:08.840
I must trouble the Eunuch

00:12.880 --> 00:14.160
Before Your Highness arrived

00:14.560 --> 00:15.760
People from the Imperial City Guard

00:16.080 --> 00:18.120
Hastily came to see His Majesty

00:18.600 --> 00:19.840
What they discussed specifically

00:20.080 --> 00:21.240
This old servant does not know

00:21.600 --> 00:22.800
Only that after they left

00:22.840 --> 00:24.520
His Majesty went to the Elixir Chamber

00:24.920 --> 00:26.320
Saying he needed to calm his mind

00:26.720 --> 00:27.880
And wait for his son

00:30.480 --> 00:31.520
Thank you, Eunuch Wen, for the reminder
